sequenceDiagram
    participant Client as External Client
    participant Gateway as Platform Ingress<br/>443/TCP HTTPS TLS 1.2+
    participant RBAC as kube-rbac-proxy<br/>8443/TCP HTTPS TLS
    participant vLLM as vLLM Container<br/>8000/TCP HTTP
    participant TGIS as vllm_tgis_adapter<br/>8033/TCP gRPC
    participant GPU as AMD Instinct GPU<br/>ROCm HIP API
    participant Storage as Model Storage<br/>PVC / S3 / HF Hub

    Note over Client,Storage: Flow 1: Model Loading (Container Startup)
    vLLM->>Storage: Load model artifacts<br/>Filesystem (PVC) or HTTPS/443 (S3/HF)
    Storage-->>vLLM: Model weights & config
    vLLM->>GPU: Transfer model to GPU VRAM<br/>HIP API (ROCm)
    GPU-->>vLLM: Model loaded in VRAM

    Note over Client,Storage: Flow 2: HTTP Inference Request (OpenAI-compatible)
    Client->>Gateway: POST /v1/chat/completions<br/>HTTPS/443, TLS 1.2+<br/>Auth: Bearer Token (platform)
    Gateway->>RBAC: Forward request<br/>HTTPS/8443, TLS<br/>Auth: Platform RBAC check
    RBAC->>vLLM: Forward request<br/>HTTP/8000 (pod-internal)<br/>Auth: None (already verified)
    vLLM->>GPU: Execute inference<br/>HIP API
    GPU-->>vLLM: Inference result
    vLLM-->>RBAC: JSON response
    RBAC-->>Gateway: Forward response
    Gateway-->>Client: JSON response<br/>HTTPS/443

    Note over Client,Storage: Flow 3: gRPC Inference Request (TGIS-compatible)
    Client->>Gateway: gRPC call<br/>HTTPS/443, TLS 1.2+<br/>Auth: Bearer Token (platform)
    Gateway->>RBAC: Forward request<br/>HTTPS/8443, TLS<br/>Auth: Platform RBAC check
    RBAC->>TGIS: Forward request<br/>gRPC/8033 (pod-internal)<br/>Auth: None (already verified)
    TGIS->>vLLM: Internal inference call
    vLLM->>GPU: Execute inference<br/>HIP API
    GPU-->>vLLM: Inference result
    vLLM-->>TGIS: Result
    TGIS-->>RBAC: gRPC response
    RBAC-->>Gateway: Forward response
    Gateway-->>Client: gRPC response<br/>HTTPS/443
